# LMS Project

A simple Learning Management System (LMS) built with **PHP**, **HTML**, and **CSS**, with **Mailtrap** integration for email testing.

## Features

- User registration and login
- Course listing and course details
- Student enrollment
- Admin or instructor management
- Form validation
- Email testing with Mailtrap
- Clean frontend built with HTML and CSS

## Technologies Used

- PHP
- HTML
- CSS
- Mailtrap

